P. (2025). &lt;span style="color:#9ea6a2"&gt;A vocabulary checklist for early lexical development in Tseltal.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;em&gt;Language Development Research, 5&lt;/em&gt;(3), 245–275.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="papers/casillas2025vocabulary.pdf" class="button" target="_blank"&gt;pdf&lt;/a&gt;
