&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Casey, K.&lt;/strong&gt;, Potter, C. E., Lew-Williams, C., &amp;amp; Wojcik, E. H. (2023). &lt;span style="color:#9ea6a2"&gt;Moving beyond “nouns in the lab”: Using naturalistic data to understand why infants’ first words include uh-oh and hi&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;em&gt;Developmental Psychology, 59&lt;/em&gt;(11), 2162-2173.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="papers/casey2023moving.pdf" class="button" target="_blank"&gt;pdf&lt;/a&gt;
